{"parentUuid":"fee52fdd-8677-4d11-8dec-5c41e28384f7","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"6c7bc17a-1146-45ad-a75a-eee684f43e7b","version":"2.1.44","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"content":[{"text":"\n\n","type":"text"}],"id":"msg_84b960a5-99ad-48ab-a4","model":"claude-opus-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":511},"cache_creation_input_tokens":511,"cache_read_input_tokens":23100,"input_tokens":52,"output_tokens":0}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"9446c2b2-3638-4b24-8821-028f858d91a4","timestamp":"2026-02-17T01:21:10.922Z"}
{"parentUuid":"9446c2b2-3638-4b24-8821-028f858d91a4","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"6c7bc17a-1146-45ad-a75a-eee684f43e7b","version":"2.1.44","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"content":[{"thinking":"\nThe user is asking how to automatically select the third model option when entering Claude Code. They want to configure Claude Code to default to a specific model.\n\nLet me think about what I know about Claude Code's model selection:\n\n1. Claude Code allows you to set the model via the `--model` flag when starting\n2. You can also set it via environment variables\n3. There's also the `/model` command within a session\n\nThe user wants to automatically select the \"third\" model option. I'm not sure exactly what the three options are in their setup, but based on the context, they're using `claude-opus-4-6[1m]` (Opus with 1M context).\n\nLet me think about the ways to configure this:\n\n1. `CLAUDE_MODEL` environment variable\n2. `--model` CLI flag\n3. Claude Code settings file\n4. `/model` command within session\n\nThe user's CLAUDE.md says they want to use `claude-opus-4-6`, so they probably want to set this as the default.\n\nLet me provide the options for auto-selecting a model in Claude Code.\n","type":"thinking","signature":""}],"id":"msg_84b960a5-99ad-48ab-a4","model":"claude-opus-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":511},"cache_creation_input_tokens":511,"cache_read_input_tokens":23100,"input_tokens":52,"output_tokens":0}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"444bdbd2-dfd2-42e2-baf8-6b66113ab5fd","timestamp":"2026-02-17T01:21:16.601Z"}
{"parentUuid":"444bdbd2-dfd2-42e2-baf8-6b66113ab5fd","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"6c7bc17a-1146-45ad-a75a-eee684f43e7b","version":"2.1.44","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"content":[{"text":"\n\n有几种方式可以让 Claude Code 启动时自动使用指定模型：\n\n**1. 环境变量（推荐）**\n\n在你的 shell 配置文件（`~/.bashrc` 或 `~/.bash_profile`）中添加：\n\n```bash\nexport ANTHROPIC_MODEL=\"claude-opus-4-6\"\n```\n\n这样每次启动 Claude Code 都会自动使用这个模型。\n\n**2. 启动时加 `--model` 参数**\n\n```bash\nclaude --model claude-opus-4-6\n```\n\n可以给它设个 alias 简化：\n\n```bash\nalias claude-opus='claude --model claude-opus-4-6'\n```\n\n**3. Claude Code 设置文件**\n\n在 `~/.claude/settings.json` 中配置：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"model\": \"claude-opus-4-6\"\n}\n```\n\n**4. 项目级别的 `.claude/settings.json`**\n\n如果只想在某个项目里用特定模型，可以在项目根目录创建 `.claude/settings.json`，格式同上。\n\n---\n\n环境变量的方式最省事，设一次就不用管了。如果你说的\"第三个\"是指 `/model` 命令弹出的列表里的第三个选项，那具体模型 ID 取决于你的列表顺序——你可以先 `/model` 看一下第三个是什么，然后用上面的方式把它设为默认。","type":"text"}],"id":"msg_84b960a5-99ad-48ab-a4","model":"claude-opus-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":52,"cache_creation_input_tokens":511,"cache_read_input_tokens":23100,"output_tokens":878,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":511},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"1afa43da-7a97-4bcb-b4a7-7cfdfbcbdc85","timestamp":"2026-02-17T01:21:23.430Z"}
